WEBVTT

00:00:26.068 --> 00:00:31.280
i čuo molbu očajnog oca robinje

00:00:31.280 --> 00:00:36.292
čiju kćerku su namjeravali 
prodati u bordel

00:00:36.302 --> 00:00:38.683
razljutio sam se.

00:00:40.423 --> 00:00:42.763
Kad sam imao 50 godina,

00:00:42.763 --> 00:00:47.586
i ležao na ulici u lokvi krvi,

00:00:47.586 --> 00:00:50.532
zajedno sa svojim sinom,

00:00:50.532 --> 00:00:52.999
razljutio sam se.

00:00:55.299 --> 00:01:00.484
Dragi moji, stoljećima nas uče 
da je ljutnja loša.